Charles N. FOLEY, Plaintiff,
v.
ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION, Defendant. SC: 157434 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 20, 2018

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, plaintiff-appellant having failed to pay the filing fee as required by the March 23, 2018 letter from the Clerk's Office, the Clerk of the Court is hereby directed to close this file.
